      *----------------준거기업등급:'00001'가산,'00001'차감
      *----------------그외는　해당무는　제외함－유석민차장요건
                              IF  WK-H-O2-ACDC-CORP-GRD-DSTCD = '00001'
                              OR  WK-H-O2-ACDC-CORP-GRD-DSTCD = '00002'
                                  PERFORM  S3340-DATA-ENTY-RTN
                                     THRU  S3340-DATA-ENTY-EXT
                              END-IF
                        WHEN  OTHER
                              MOVE  SPACE
                                TO  XZUGEROR-I-TBL-ID
                              MOVE  SPACE
                                TO  XZUGEROR-I-FUNC-CD
                              MOVE  SQLCODE
                                TO  XZUGEROR-I-SQL-CD
                              MOVE  'DATA CALCULATE ERROR'
                                TO  XZUGEROR-I-MSG
