      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3340-DATA-ENTY-RTN.

           INITIALIZE    OT-REC

      *   그룹회사코드
           MOVE  WK-H-I-GROUP-CO-CD
             TO  RJL0025-GROUP-CO-CD

      *   계좌번호
           MOVE  WK-H-O1-FC-PRDCT-PTRN-DSTCD
             TO  RJL0025-ACNO(1:3)
           MOVE  WK-H-O1-FC-TRAN-NO
             TO  RJL0025-ACNO(4:13)

