       S7000-SELECT-GOGAKEX-RTN.
----->*아래 항목정의 필요
      *입력항목:여신종류구분,계좌관리부실점,고객고유번호
      *출력항목:고객고유번호，모기업법인등록번호，계좌적용구분
      *           해외현지법인여부

           INITIALIZE    XBJLCUST-CA

      *--       그룹회사코드
           MOVE  WK-H-I-GROUP-CO-CD
             TO  XBJLCUST-I-GROUP-CO-CD

      *--       여신종류구분　
           MOVE  '2'
             TO  XBJLCUST-I-YSGB

      *--       관리부실점코드
           MOVE  WK-H-O2-BRNCD
             TO  XBJLCUST-I-BRCD

      *--       주민번호및법인등록번호
           MOVE  WK-H-O2-ACDC-CI-BRWR-NO
             TO  XBJLCUST-I-BRWR-NO

      *주민번호및법인등록번호가없으면＇기타＇로　적용
           IF  WK-H-O2-ACDC-CI-BRWR-NO = SPACES
           THEN
      *        계좌적용구분
               MOVE  '9'
                 TO  RJL0025-ACN-APLY-DSTCD

      *        해외현지법인여부
               MOVE  '0'
                 TO  RJL0025-OVSES-LCAL-COPR-YN

           ELSE

               #DYCALL  BJLCUST YCCOMMON-CA XBJLCUST-CA

               IF  NOT COND-XBJLCUST-OK
                   #ERROR  XBJLCUST-R-ERRCD
                           XBJLCUST-R-TREAT-CD
                           XBJLCUST-R-STAT
                   #OKEXIT CO-CHA-08
               END-IF

      *        차주번호
               MOVE  XBJLCUST-O-MAMA-CORPNO
                 TO  RJL0025-BRWR-NO

      *        계좌적용구분
               MOVE  XBJLCUST-O-GJGB
                 TO  RJL0025-ACN-APLY-DSTCD

      *        해외현지법인여부
               MOVE  XBJLCUST-O-HWGB
                 TO  RJL0025-OVSES-LCAL-COPR-YN
           END-IF
           .
       S7000-SELECT-GOGAKEX-EXT.
           EXIT.
