       S8000-BJLTGEX-CALL-RTN.

           INITIALIZE    XBJLTGEX-CA

      *@1.1.1 입력파라미터 조립
      *          처리구분(1:통화별환산2:외환매매익역환산)
           MOVE  WK-GBCD               TO  XBJLTGEX-I-GBCD
